item.description:
@pr1v4cy wrote:

not sure if it will work on your server but if you open client.java and search for

sendFrame126

you should see

sendFrame126("Bank", 180);//frist emote slot

and just get rid of the emote things you dont want

mine is

sendFrame126("Bank", 180);//frist emote slot sendFrame126("Dummys",181); sendFrame126("Varr", 178); sendFrame126("Fally",175); sendFrame126("Lumby",177); sendFrame126("Ardy",182); }

and if you remove oh idk ardy then it should look like this

sendFrame126("Bank", 180);//frist emote slot sendFrame126("Dummys",181); sendFrame126("Varr", 178); sendFrame126("Fally",175); sendFrame126("Lumby",177); }

so ya i hope i helped you out alittle atleast
